- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of advanced techniques to improve the performance of natural language generation tasks falls under the scope of cs.AI. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed architecture involves the use of neural networks, which is a common theme in cs.NE.
